Hilarious to see Michael Bolton for the final song. It was heavy on cliches, but that worked for it. I hope Andy Samberg continues to make great comedy, away from The Lonely Island, and Brooklyn Nine-Nine. I think the team up with Judd Apatow was great for production, and most of the trailer scenes were at the start, so not much of the key scenes and plot points were given away. Bery much enjoyed this movie. If i were to do it like grades, it would be a B+.
